<lyrics>[V1]
 1- kạnt ḥyạty ngẖmẗ ḥzynẗ
 mlyạnẗ ạ̉wjạʿ wjrwḥ dfynẗ
 ḥd wgẖyrh wʿyn sẖryrẗ srqẗ wsẖtymẗ bạ̉lfạẓ
 mryrẗ
 wạ̹ydyn ṭwylẗ ʿly̱ ạlkẖlyqẗ wạ̉yạm dẖlylẗ fy sjn
 ạlkẖṭyẗ
 ạlqrạr- lkn hw ʿdy̱ ʿly wqạl ly ạtbʿny fjạ̉ẗ
 lqyt sẖkẖṣ byrfʿny wyrfʿny
 wnẓr ly bʿynh ạlḥlwẗ ạlly dwbt wqạl ly tʿạl
 ạtbʿny mạ tkẖạfsẖ yạ
 qlby wldy wạ̉nạ fjạ̉ẗ lqyt ḥb wḥbyt sẖkẖṣ yḥb
 mạ yʿrf ykrh ḥty̱ ạ̉ʿdạw̉h fj bnwrh jwạ fy
 qlby gẖyr ḥạlẗ
 2- rậny mwjwd ʿnd ạljbạyẗ myt wkạnt hy ạlnhạyẗ
 ạ̹nsạn ḍlạly gẖsẖạn ḥrạmy ạlqrsẖ ạ̉bwyạ wạlkdẖb
 ḥlạly
 sẖfq lḥạly wqạl tʿạl ly dạ ạ̹nt fy bạly wʿly̱
 qlby gẖạly</lyrics>
